ion. The firm prefers to make seed capital funding in infrastructure projects in the range of $2 million and $10 million. In the real estate sector, it seeks to invest between $20 million and $50 million. The firm seeks to hold its investments for a period between three years and five years. It seeks to make private equity investments in post revenue companies. The firm prefers to take a seat on the board of directors of its portfolio companies. IL&FS Investment Managers Limited was founded in 1989 and is based in Mumbai, India. It operates as a subsidiary of Infrastructure Leasing & Financial Services Limited", "fullTimeEmployees": 16, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Lubna Ahmad Usman", "age": 52, "title": "CEO, CFO & Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1973, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 80000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Kamalesh  Sarangi", "age": 53, "title": "Senior Vice President", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Prasad Prakash Chaoji", "title": "Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Charlene  Fernandes", "age": 51, "title": "Manager", "yearBorn": 1974, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Giselle  Fernandes", "age": 52, "title": "Manager", "yearBorn": 1973, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Swapneel  Desai", "age": 43, "title": "Senior Manager", "yearBorn": 1982, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Arvind  Iyengar", "age": 46, "title": "Senior Manager", "yearBorn": 1979, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mona  Abhani", "age": 38, "title": "Senior Manager", "yearBorn": 1987, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedVal